= SDL_iPhoneSetEventPump =
Use this function to enable or disable the SDL event pump on Apple iOS.




== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_iPhoneSetEventPump(SDL_bool enabled)
```


== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''enabled'''
|SDL_TRUE to enable the event pump, SDL_FALSE to disable it
|}


